room_title: Escape room "The Haunting of Madam Delilah" by Escape Point in Minot
room_description: The infamous Madam Delilah was known for predicting the future, but you don't believe in magic! Determined to prove her wrong, you schedule a reading with her. But something goes terribly wrong... The gypsy has transported you to another dimension! Can you find a way back in order to save your souls or will you be trapped as yet another victim of the enigmatic fortuneteller?
